r />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你聽到新聞官點喝止香港電台記者？<br />\n<br />\n叫佢唔好打斷<span style=\"color: red;\">行政長官</span>發言<br />\n<br />\n強調<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行政長官</span>係仍想訴諸權威<br />\n<br />\n畀崇尚權威嘅藍絲聽 覺得我哋冇禮貌不尊重規矩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">權威？其實冇人民認可嘅權威只係威權<br />\n<br />\n</span>記者要逆權，一定一定一定要<br />\n打斷所有高官政治宣傳式發言及回應<br />\n揭露佢哋偽善 欺騙香港人真面目</span>"},{"pid":"5c64857ff46220341f5daace6424320962dbbca7","tid":1458124,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"出去阿"},{"pid":"f52db73e8e8e5204de1a1e0ad2a78898ef64a760","tid":1458124,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"推阿屌"},{"pid":"207d8e7f43fd00f4894b3f196a3120b8e3852e4b","tid":1458124,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"過黎未阿？"},{"pid":"d51b04fd401c6c5c1d9f2ffe77eb1cbf574113d8","tid":1458124,"uid":294831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"收工入呀 等我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632f6679dc670d005778726e696b2f516cda75d8","tid":1458124,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"唔夠人阿屌"}]}